  "text": "Our work is similar to Baidu research [CITATION_1] where a bidirectional RNN is used to speed up the speech recognition performance using GPU (Graphics Processing Unit) parallelization. We have used a single GPU structure for our experiments to evaluate and compare the results of three recurrent networks, namely bidirectional RNN, bidirectional LSTM, and bidirectional GRU.",
